#Requirements
### Non-Functional
1.	It should take less than 10 minutes to understand and be able to play this game.
2.	Response time should be less than 2 seconds.

### Functional
1.	It is a text based game.
2.	It has a combat system.
3.	It has an inventory system.
4.	It is possible to move between stages.
5.	Includes help to explain different aspects of the game, such as possible commands.
6.	Has a save function.
7.	Capable of loading different level (Maps) or save files.
8.	Can have custom (user made) content (Objects/Maps/Monsters).
9.	Has multiple game modes.
